{% extends "layouts/standard_content.jinja" %}
{% from "components/heading.jinja" import heading %}
{% from "components/card.jinja" import card %}
{% from "components/contents.jinja" import contents %}
{% from "components/link.jinja" import link %}
{% from "components/list.jinja" import list, list_item %}
{% block mobile_article_title %}
  {% call heading() %}
    Courts and date coverage
  {% endcall %}
  <p>
    Different courts and tribunals have different coverage on Find Case Law. Some have
    comprehensive recent records, while others include selected historical judgments.
  </p>
{% endblock mobile_article_title %}
{% block desktop_article_title %}
  {% call heading() %}
    Courts and date coverage
  {% endcall %}
  <p>
    Different courts and tribunals have different coverage on Find Case Law. Some have
    comprehensive recent records, while others include selected historical judgments.
  </p>
{% endblock desktop_article_title %}
{% block article_navigation %}
  {% call contents(title="On this page") %}
    {% call list() %}
      {% call list_item() %}
        {% call link(href="#why-coverage-varies") %}
          Why coverage varies
        {% endcall %}
      {% endcall %}
      {% call list_item() %}
        {% call link(href="#understanding-our-coverage") %}
          Understanding our coverage
        {% endcall %}
      {% endcall %}
      {% call list_item() %}
        {% call link(href="#using-coverage-information") %}
          Using coverage information
        {% endcall %}
      {% endcall %}
      {% call list_item() %}
        {% call link(href="#coverage-is-expanding") %}
          Coverage is expanding
        {% endcall %}
      {% endcall %}
    {% endcall %}
  {% endcall %}
{% endblock article_navigation %}
{% block article_content %}
  {% call heading(tag="h2") %}
    Why coverage varies
  {% endcall %}
  <p>The coverage we provide depends on different factors:</p>
  {% call list(variant="bullets") %}
    {% call list_item() %}
      court digitisation – when courts began creating digital records
    {% endcall %}
    {% call list_item() %}
      publication practices – how different courts decide what to publish
    {% endcall %}
  {% endcall %}
  <p>
    Understanding these variations helps you know what to expect when searching and whether the case you're looking for should be in our collection.
  </p>
  {% call heading(tag="h2") %}
    Understanding our coverage
  {% endcall %}
  <p>
    {%- call link(href=url("courts_and_tribunals_in_fcl")) -%}
      Courts and tribunals in Find Case Law
    {%- endcall %}
    provides detailed coverage information for each court and tribunal, including:
  </p>
  {% call list(variant="bullets") %}
    {% call list_item() %}
      date ranges for each court's records
    {% endcall %}
    {% call list_item() %}
      how complete the coverage is
    {% endcall %}
    {% call list_item() %}
      what types of cases are included
    {% endcall %}
    {% call list_item() %}
      notes on special collections or historical records
    {% endcall %}
  {% endcall %}
  {% call heading(tag="h2") %}
    Using coverage information
  {% endcall %}
  <p>Knowing the coverage helps you:</p>
  {% call list(variant="bullets") %}
    {% call list_item() %}
      search more effectively – understanding what's available prevents frustration when cases don't appear
    {% endcall %}
    {% call list_item() %}
      set realistic expectations – some courts have gaps in their records
    {% endcall %}
    {% call list_item() %}
      find alternatives – if coverage is limited, we can point you to other sources
    {% endcall %}
    {% call list_item() %}
      understand the collection – see how Find Case Law has grown and continues to expand
    {% endcall %}
  {% endcall %}
  {% call heading(tag="h2") %}
    Coverage is expanding
  {% endcall %}
  <p>
    We regularly add new courts, extend date ranges for existing courts, and digitise historical
    judgments. The coverage information is updated as we expand the service.
  </p>
  <p>
    If you can't find what you're looking for, check the coverage details to see whether it falls within our current scope.
  </p>
{% endblock article_content %}
